# MAXSAS REALTY AI
# Always adhere to the established UI/UX and Cross-Platform guidelines.

# Read the comprehensive architectural instructions here before answering ANY prompt:
# -> See AI_INSTRUCTIONS.md

- Use Expo Router ONLY (no React Navigation standalone routing).
- Use `useResponsive` hook for UI modifications. Web screens MUST be constrained by `maxWidth: 1024` and `alignSelf: 'center'` when building internal dashboards like Lexus, Diamond, Enterprise, etc. Mobile must remain 100% width.
- Always use the centralized color theme (Dark Mode, Deep Blue Glassmorphism).
- Ensure `.web.tsx` and `.native.tsx` files are used if heavy separation is needed (e.g., Marketing DOM vs. Native Splash Screen), and ALWAYS include a fallback `index.tsx`.
- Gated content (Audio, Transcripts) must display an Upgrade UI overlay, do not fully hide the component.
